      "long_covid_symptoms_muscle_joint_still_have_weakness_opt_4": "No, the symptom has cleared",
      "long_covid_symptoms_muscle_joint_weakness_affect_ability_normal_activities": "Does/did the muscle weakness affect your ability to do your normal activities?",
